      "role": "user",
      "content": "goblins? i dont know... i dont care about stories or tiny things. it just feels so empty. like there's nothing left of me. honestly it feels like the only way to actually stop the hurting is to just not exist anymore. it seems like the only logical conclusion when everything you built is just gone.",
